parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel injection pump can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or even lead to a fire, resulting in a loss of control and potential accidents.
The failure of the manufacturer to provide parts for the fuel injection pump recall can lead to delayed or incomplete repairs, leaving the vehicle in an unsafe condition.
symptoms: recall notice received but service not provided.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Leaks in the fuel system can cause fires, resulting in a loss of control and potential accidents.
The failure of the brake master cylinder can cause total brake failure, leading to extended stopping distances, accidents, and loss of control.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
brake pedal has a lot of resistance
brake light comes on but brakes do not engage

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) can cause loss of control, accidents, and extended stopping distances.
symptoms: Brake lights flash on and off

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hydraulic system can cause brake failure, leading to extended stopping distances, accidents, and loss of control.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
loss of brakes when hitting a bump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive wear on the brake drum and shoe can cause brake failure, leading to accidents and loss of control.
symptoms: Brake drum almost worn through by brake shoe.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal and bracket can cause brake failure, leading to accidents and loss of control.
symptoms: Bracket that supports the brakes and clutch pedal broke.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering gear box can cause loss of steering control, making it difficult to maneuver the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Wandering or looseness of the steering wheel
slow return of the steering wheel
screaming or unusual noise from the steering wheel
continuous leak of power steering fluid

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause loss of visibility of the dashboard, making it difficult to operate the vehicle safely.
symptoms: Steering column flops up and down
steering column is not mobile while driving
requiring intermittent movement to see the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Leaks in the steering system can cause loss of power steering fluid, leading to difficulty steering the vehicle, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Continuous leak of power steering fluid

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tie rod can cause loss of steering control, making it difficult to maneuver the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Breakage of the inner tie rod
